org.opends.server.admin.std.client

Interface FractionalLDIFImportPluginCfgClient

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigurationClient, PluginCfgClient

    public interface FractionalLDIFImportPluginCfgClient
extends PluginCfgClient
    A client-side interface for reading and modifying Fractional LDIF Import Plugin settings.

    The Fractional LDIF Import Plugin is used internally by the replication plugin to support fractional replication.
